* The little kitten bounced around in the small, dark compartment, his bum 
hitting one ofthe walls, his wings the roof and his soft, furry head the 
compartment door.*

"Meeorrww!"

* He disliked it in here. Alot. He scratched at the door, he wanted OUT! 
again he was banged around, and again he made a squeeking noise.*

" Eeeeeeep!"

* He did a flip and landed on his head, his butt on the roof. He sighed in a 
cute way. He really didn't like it in here.*
